YTLite: Android Native Architecture & Product Specification
1. Project Overview & Target
App Name: YTLite

Target Platform: Android (Min SDK 24 / Android 7.0+)

Development Language: 100% Kotlin

UI Framework: Jetpack Compose (Declarative UI)

Core Philosophy: Local-First & Performance-Driven for Low-End Devices. Zero ads, background playback, fully native UI rendering, completely decoupled from official YouTube/Google Play Services.

2. Technical Stack & Architecture
Plaintext
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|               UI Layer (Jetpack Compose)                    |
|   (Home Feed / Search / Player View / Library View / Shorts)|
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
                              |
                              v
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|                 ViewModel & State Management                |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
                              |
                              v
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
